title: JIGSAW PUZZLE DELUXE
description: Relax after a stressful day and enjoy this beautiful jigsaw puzzle game! More than 300 amazing images offer you a great variety of different themes and moods. No matter if you like nature, animals, art or food - simply select the picture you like best and start puzzling! Customize your puzzle by selecting the amount of pieces, turning on rotation mode or turning off the preview mode if you prefer a challenge. Hours of relaxing fun guaranteed!
